name: rubics
description: U2 ,U' , U - Turn the top (up) face clockwise. D2 ,D' , D - Turn the bottom (down) face clockwise. R2 ,R' , R - Turn the right face clockwise. L2 ,L' , L - Turn the left face clockwise. F2 ,F' , F - Turn the front face clockwise. B2 ,B' , B - Turn the back face clockwise
